Chapter~\ref{chap:acid} presents [[main()]], the REPL,
the initialization sequence, and process attachment.
%
Chapter~\ref{chap:libmach} presents [[libmach]], the library for
parsing executables, loading symbol tables, and disassembling
instructions, and how [[acid]] uses it.
